# 클라이언트 배포 설정

## 개발 환경 (.env.development)

```env
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000
VITE_CLIENT_URL=http://localhost:3000
```

## 프로덕션 환경 (.env.production)

```env
# Render 배포 시
VITE_API_URL=https://your-icondb-server.onrender.com
VITE_CLIENT_URL=https://your-frontend-url.com

# Railway 배포 시
VITE_API_URL=https://your-railway-service-url
VITE_CLIENT_URL=https://your-frontend-url.com

# Vercel 배포 시
VITE_API_URL=https://your-server-api-url
VITE_CLIENT_URL=https://your-vercel-url.vercel.app
```

## Vite에서 사용

```javascript
// src/config/api.js
const API_URL = import.meta.env.VITE_API_URL || 'http://localhost:5000';

export const apiClient = axios.create({
  baseURL: API_URL,
  timeout: 5000,
  withCredentials: true,
});
```

## 자동 배포 설정 (GitHub Actions)

`.github/workflows/deploy.yml`

```yaml
name: Deploy to Render

on:
  push:
    branches: [main]

jobs:
  deploy:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v2
      
      - name: Deploy to Render
        uses: render-org/render-github-action@v0
        with:
          service-id: ${{ secrets.RENDER_SERVICE_ID }}
          api-token: ${{ secrets.RENDER_API_TOKEN }}
```
